OL,3,CWarning of 'extreme risk' over first
OL,4,Cbudget proposed by Reform council
OL,6,FReform UK's "flagship" local authority
OL,7,Fin Kent has been accused of proposing
OL,8,Fa budget of "extreme risk" and one
OL,9,Fthat is "potentially reckless" by
OL,10,Fopposition leaders ahead of a vote on
OL,11,Fthe financial plans.
OL,13,FThe latest budget will be the first
OL,14,Funder a Reform-led Kent County Council
OL,15,Fsince Reform came to power after local
OL,16,Felections in May last year.
