OL,3,CWarning of 'extreme risk' over first
OL,4,Cbudget proposed by Reform council
OL,6,FOpposition parties have warned against
OL,7,F"dangerously low" reserves and the
OL,8,Fauthority's "highest ever exposure to
OL,9,Ffinancial risk" totalling more than
OL,10,F#410 million on the risk register.
OL,12,FKent's Reform leaders have already
OL,13,Fproposed a 3.99% council tax increase,
OL,14,F1% under the limit before a referendum
OL,15,Fis required, despite promising ahead
OL,16,Fof their election victory not to raise
OL,17,Ftax.
