OL,3,CWarning of 'extreme risk' over first
OL,4,Cbudget proposed by Reform council
OL,6,FCouncil leader Linden Kemkaran said
OL,7,FReform would prefer not to propose a
OL,8,Fcouncil tax increase at all but given
OL,9,F"the dire legacy we inherited"
OL,10,Falongside an unprecedented rise in
OL,11,Fdemands and costs for services such as
OL,12,Fsocial care, "this is simply not
OL,13,Fpossible".
OL,15,FBut opposition bosses have criticised
OL,16,Fthe move for not raising it to the
OL,17,Fmaximum possible, which will leave the
OL,18,Fcouncil with #10 million less for the
OL,19,Fnext financial year that could have
OL,20,Fprotected services and reserves.
