OL,6,FThey also pointed to a statement from
OL,7,Fthe council's head of finance David
OL,8,FShipton, legally required to be
OL,9,Fconsidered for the budget, where he
OL,10,Fsaid: "The decision to raise the
OL,11,Fcouncil tax household charge below the
OL,12,Flevel permitted without a referendum
OL,13,Fposes a long-term financial risk as a
OL,14,Fresult of the council tax income
OL,15,Fforgone."
