OL,6,FIn Mr Shipton's statement, called
OL,7,FSection 25 assurance, it also said the
OL,8,Flevel of forecast overspend for this
OL,9,Ffinancial year poses a "significant
OL,10,Frisk" to the council's reserves and
OL,11,Ffinancial sustainability.
OL,13,FIt added: "Without improvement there
OL,14,Fis a risk that the general reserve
OL,15,Favailable in 2026/27 would be below
OL,16,Fthe recommended 5% to 10% target
OL,17,Frange."
