OL,14,Fdescribed it as a "real gambler's
OL,15,Fbudget" while Labour's chief Alister
OL,16,FBrady said Kent County Council was
OL,17,F"heading for financial danger" under
OL,18,FReform.
OL,20,FBut Ms Kemkaran said: "This is a
OL,21,Fresponsible budget.
